#. Description of the theme
msgid "A WordPress theme for financial research publishers — the investment research firms, economic think tanks, and capital markets publications that lead with data, not decoration. IBM Plex Serif for editorial authority, IBM Plex Sans for interface precision, IBM Plex Mono for every number. The data table is the hero. Built on the Colophon core: WCAG 2.2 AA accessibility guidance, Core Web Vitals optimised, self-hosted SIL OFL fonts, RTL-ready via CSS logical properties, zero plugin dependencies."
msgstr ""

